        <div class="section">
            <h2>Final Pro Tips for 2026</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Use job-specific keywords → pass ATS filters</li>
                <li>Quantify when possible (tools, certifications, CGPA if strong)</li>
                <li>Write fresh version for every application</li>
                <li>Place it right after contact details</li>
            </ul>
